						<h3 itemprop="name" class="not-hidden">
					About Us			</h3>
		<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Morara Apiemi &amp; Company Advocates was established in 2001 and the partnership later merged in 2009 with Oenga, W. Nyangito &amp; Company Advocates. Morara Apiemi &amp; Nyangito Company Advocates is founded on the following principles and objectives.</p>
<p>i) To provide consistent quality and prompt legal services in the East African Region and all over the world.</p>
<p>ii) Strict adherence to professional codes of conduct.</p>
<p>iii) Ensuring fundamental relationship of trust and confidentiality, which distinguishes the profession of legal services from that of other consultancy services.</p>
<p>iv) To provide high quality legal services focusing on the satisfaction of the need of both corporate and individual clients.</p> 	</div>

	
	
				
	
	
